<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Khrihfa tho u, it ti hlah, Tahnak kan dinhtak lai maw? A nawl a kan
 pek lioah, Kan thu sawhsawh ko lai maw?

[C1]
   Kal law tuan (kal law tuan) hramthawk cang hen, (hramthawk cang hen)
   Kal law kawl, (kal law kal) a tlaumi hna, (a tlawm hna) Sual muih
   si-fahnak chungin, Rawldanghnak ah hun hruai hna.

[V2]
 Khamhtu kan daw taktak maw? A biakam kan zum kho maw? Kan zeizong kan
 pe siang maw? A bia kan ngai lai lo maw?

[C2]
   Kal law tuan (kal law tuan) hramthawk cang hen, (hramthawk cang hen)
   Kal law kawl, (kal law kal) a tlaumi hna, (a tlawm hna) Sual muih
   si-fahnak chungin, Rawldanghnak ah hun hruai hna.

[V3]
 Zumh hnga tluk in kan zum maw? A chim bangin kan nung maw? Amah ta
 lawng kan si maw? Zumhnak cu rian ah lang seh.

[C3]
   Kal law tuan (kal law tuan) hramthawk cang hen, (hramthawk cang hen)
   Kal law kawl, (kal law kal) a tlaumi hna, (a tlawm hna) Sual muih
   si-fahnak chungin, Rawldanghnak ah hun hruai hna.

[V4]
 Kan put hnga vai-lamtah cu, Sui luchin ruahchan ahcun; Teima tein tuan
 cio u, Caan a tawi ni a tlawm cang.

[C4]
   Kal law tuan (kal law tuan) hramthawk cang hen, (hramthawk cang hen)
   Kal law kawl, (kal law kal) a tlaumi hna, (a tlawm hna) Sual muih
   si-fahnak chungin, Rawldanghnak ah hun hruai hna.</lyrics>
